
  Groudon    Ground Type Pokémon

  GROUDON has long been described 
  in  mythology as the Pokémon 
  that raised lands and expanded 
  continents.  Groudon took 
  to sleep after a cataclysmic 
  battle with KYOGRE. 
  Single Stage Evolution Pokémon

